_____________________________________________
Page Object Model (POM)
Instead of writing locators inside test classes:
Use POM:

LoginPage.java

@FindBy(id="email")
@FindBy(id="password")
@FindBy(id="login")

Benefits
Reusable code
Easier maintenance
Cleaner tests
Better scalability
